# OTA Framework Integration Guide

## Overview

This guide covers integrating the OTA (Over-The-Air) update framework into
your embedded product. The framework provides A/B slot partitioning, delta
updates, automatic rollback on boot failure, cryptographic signature
verification, and server-side phased rollout.

## Prerequisites

- CORE-05 (Skill Pack Framework) installed and validated
- CORE-15 (Security Stack) for key management and secure boot chain

