## Quick Start

1. Choose your A/B slot scheme based on target SoC
2. Generate signing keypair: `openssl genpkey -algorithm ed25519 -out ota.key`
3. Configure RAUC `system.conf` (Linux) or MCUboot keys (MCU)
4. Implement health check in your application
5. Set up OTA server with manifest endpoint
6. Test full cycle: flash -> reboot -> verify -> rollback path
